These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, time-travel, horror
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching horror movies##7
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | satire | horror | crime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, ritmeester, vegafina, game
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##7
3. the vegafina-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the game-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | game | vegafina | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, chestnut, brown, red
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes red is somewhere between the person who likes brown and the person who likes chestnut##7
3. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | grey | chestnut | red | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, go, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person playing go and the person playing whist##7
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | go | canasta | scrabble | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, poker, domino
1. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing bridge and the person playing domino##2
3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person playing domino##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Game   | poker | bridge | mah-jongg | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking almond-milk##7
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | 7up | soy-milk |

