2. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Sport   | biathlon | lacrosse | basketball | weightlifting |

