.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, horse, fish, chinchilla
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the bird##5
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the fish##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Pet   | fish | bird | chinchilla | horse |

